item.title: CVE-2024-9141|2024-09-24T10:50:25.810Z -- oct8ne -- oct8ne
item.description: Cross-Site Scripting (XSS) vulnerability in the Oct8ne system. This flaw could allow an attacker to embed harmful JavaScript code into the body of a chat message. This manipulation occurs when the chat content is intercepted and altered, leading to the execution of the JavaScript payload.
